item.title: Script Review: Dax Combat v2 Beta - TRiBot
item.description: Dax Combat v2 Beta is a popular Oldschool Runescape combat script for TRiBot. It has an optimized combat system, utilizes Dax’s powerful webwalker, and has everything a basic fighter needs.
